The paper focuses on visual dialog, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Additionally, the paper proposes a new model for multi-step reasoning, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques, making it relevant to the machine learning (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
